---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Neon Injector"
  description="Review the terms and conditions for using Neon Injector, including user responsibilities and usage guidelines."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Terms of Service</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-4">By using Neon Injector, you agree to comply with the following terms and conditions, which govern your use of our tool and services.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Usage Guidelines</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use Neon Injector.</li>
            <li>Neon Injector is for personal, non-commercial use only.</li>
            <li>Do not use Neon Injector to engage in activities that violate Mobile Legends’ Terms of Service.</li>
            <li>Do not attempt to reverse-engineer or modify Neon Injector’s code.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">2. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>You are solely responsible for any risks associated with using Neon Injector, including potential account bans.</li>
            <li>Do not distribute modified or unofficial versions of Neon Injector.</li>
            <li>Promptly report any bugs or issues to our support team via <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3. Liability</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Neon Injector is provided “as is” without warranties of any kind. The Neon Injector team is not liable for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Damages or losses resulting from the use of our tool.</li>
            <li>Account suspensions or bans by Moonton or Mobile Legends.</li>
            <li>Any interruptions or errors in the tool’s functionality.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4. Termination</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We reserve the right to terminate access to Neon Injector for users who violate these terms or engage in harmful activities.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>.</p>
          <img src="/images/terms-agreement.webp" alt="Terms Agreement" class="w-full rounded-lg mt-8" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>